com.sterlingcommerce.baseutil

Class SCPropertyManagerFactoryService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.baseutil.SCPropertyManagerFactoryService

  • public class SCPropertyManagerFactoryService
extends java.lang.Object
    A service class to get an implementation of ISCPropertyManagerFactory The default behavior is to return an instance of class com.sterlingcommerce.woodstock.util.frame.SCIPropertyManagerFactory. It can be overridden by explicitly setting an instance by invoking setFactory(String)

      • setFactory

        public void setFactory(java.lang.String className)
        The SCPropertyManagerFactoryService supports injection of a Factory via the setFactory method. If the method has been called, subsequent calls to the service will return the type that was last injected.
        Parameters:
        className - Name of the class that implements ISCPropertyManagerFactory

      • getFactory

        public ISCPropertyManagerFactory getFactory()
        The SCPropertyManagerFactoryService provides a getFactory method that returns an implementation of the ISCPropertyManagerFactory interface. If the setFactory method has been called, the implementation passed to the method call is used. Otherwise, it defaults to returning a com.sterlingcommerce.woodstock.util.frame.SCIPropertyManagerFactory instance.
        Returns:
        an implementation of ISCPropertyManagerFactory interface
